### ==========================================
### WeatherStation API Documentation
### Base URL (Production)
### ==========================================

@baseUrl = https://ws-functions-prod.azurewebsites.net

### ==========================================
### 1️ Start a new image generation job
### ==========================================

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/jobs
Content-Type: application/json

###

### ==========================================
### 2️ Get job status 
### ==========================================

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/jobs/c79dc39b-f994-4fc2-a580-780344679098

###

### ==========================================
### Example Workflow
### ==========================================
### 1. Run POST /api/jobs
### 2. Copy returned jobId
### 3. Replace {{jobId}} below
### 4. Call GET /api/jobs/{{jobId}}
### 5. Wait until status = Completed
### 6. Open image URLs returned in response
